What this script does

Removes the default Nginx page.

Configures full node + multiple lite nodes in Nginx.

Obtains HTTPS SSL certificates for all nodes automatically.

Installs the latest Node.js LTS automatically.

Sets up systemd services for all nodes.

Adds firewall, Fail2Ban, SSH hardening, admin user, and auto-updates.

Provides a single admin update script for all nodes

