This version:

Automatically removes the default Nginx page.

Configures Nginx for the full node (yourdomain.com) and multiple lite nodes (lite1.yourdomain.com, lite2.yourdomain.com, …).

Requests SSL certificates for all nodes via Certbot.

Ensures full + lite nodes are served properly over HTTPS.

Works together with the latest Node.js LTS installation, firewall, Fail2Ban, systemd services, and admin update script.

